3.00	Pepperbox	Pepper-box	The pepper-box revolver or simply pepperbox (also "pepper-pot", from its resemblance to the household pepper grinder) is a multiple-barrel repeating firearm that has three or more barrels grouped around a central axis. It mostly appears in the form of a multi-shot handheld firearm. Pepperboxes exist in all ammunition systems: matchlock, wheellock, flintlock, percussion, pinfire, rimfire and centerfire.	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/2/26/Pepperbox_tula3.jpg/220px-Pepperbox_tula3.jpg
